title: Who Watches the Watchmen - Complete Soundtrack
description:
"Who Watches the Watchmen" - Complete Soundtrack
================================================

01 - Muse - Take a Bow
02 - Smashing Pumpkins - The Beginning Is The End Is The Beginning
03 - Nat King Cole - Unforgettable
04 - Bob Dylan - The times they are a changin
05 - Nena - 99 Luftballons
06 - Simon and Garfunkel - The sound of silence
07 - Budapest Symphony Orchestra - Ride of the Valkyries
08 - Janis Joplin - Me and Bobby Mc Gee
09 - K.C. and the Sunshine Band - Im Your Boogie Man
10 - Billie Holiday - You're my thrill
11 - The Philip Glass Ensemble - Pruit igoe and prophecies
12 - Tears for Fears - Everybody Wants To Rule The World
13 - Leonard Cohen - Hallelujah
14 - Waylon Jennings - Clyde
15 - Jimi Hendrix - All along the Watchtower
16 - My Chemical Romance - Desolation Row
17 - Leonard Cohen - First We Take Manhattan
18 - Nina Simone - Pirate Jenny

This compilation was made by "io" for all who watches the movie and enjoy it in some degree.
The original OST lacks of some important tracks, and this "Who Watches the Watchmen" - Complete Soundtrack is as far as I know the 1st and only complete soundtrack of the movie. Every theme was ordered following the order of the movie.

Buy the comics, buy movie DVD.

"io"
